SELECT Orders.PPropertyId, Tenants.TenantId, Tenants.TenantName, Tenants.TenantNo, Tenants.TenantVatNo, Tenants.TenantAccountReference, Tenants.TenantWebsite, Tenants.TenantDayPhone, Tenants.TenantEveningPhone, Tenants.TenantMobilePhone, Tenants.TenantFax, Tenants.TenantAddress1, Tenants.TenantAddress2, Tenants.TenantAddress3, Tenants.TenantAddress4, Tenants.TenantCity, Tenants.TenantStateCounty, Tenants.CurrencyID, Tenants.CountryID, GlobalCurrency.CurrencyName, GlobalCountries.CountryName, Accounts.AccountID, Accounts.AccountCode, Accounts.CompanyName AS AcCompanyName, Accounts.CountryID AS AccountCountryId, Accounts.CurrencyID AS AccountCurrencyId, Accounts.AccountStatusID, Accounts.PriceGroupID, Accounts.VATNo, Accounts.RegNo, Accounts.AccountEmail AS AcEmail, Accounts.Telephone AS AcTelephone, Accounts.Mobile AS AcMobile, Accounts.website AS AcWebsite, Accounts.CreditLimit AS AcLimit, Accounts.AccountTypeCustomer, Accounts.AccountTypeSupplier, Accounts.AccountTypeEndUser, Orders.OrderID, Orders.OrderNumber, Orders.IssueDate, CAST(Orders.ExpectedDate AS date) AS Expr1, Orders.Note, Orders.ReportTypeChargeId, Orders.InventoryTransactionTypeId, Orders.AccountID AS OrderAccountId, Orders.OrderTotal + COALESCE (CAST(Orders.OrderCost AS DECIMAL(9, 2)), 0) AS OrderGrandTotal, AccountAddresses.AccountID AS AcAccountID, AccountAddresses.AddressLine1 AS AcAddressLine1, AccountAddresses.AddressLine2 AS AcAddressLine2, AccountAddresses.AddressLine3 AS AcAddressLine3, AccountAddresses.CountryID AS AccountAddressCountry, AccountAddresses.AddressID, Tenants.TenantPostalCode, AccountAddresses.PostCode AS AcPostCode, Orders.OrderTotal, SLAPriorits.Priority, SLAPriorits.Description, Orders.PPropertyId AS Expr2, Orders.ExpectedHours, TenantLocations.WarehouseId AS TenantWarehouseId, TenantLocations.WarehouseName AS TenantWarehouseName, TenantLocations.AddressLine1 AS TenantWarehouseAddr1, TenantLocations.AddressLine2 AS TenantWarehouseAddr2, TenantLocations.AddressLine3 AS TenantWarehouseAddr3, TenantLocations.CountyState AS TenantWarehouseCounty, TenantLocations.PostalCode AS TenantWarehousePostcode, TenantWarehouse.WarehouseId AS ToWarehouseId, TenantWarehouse.WarehouseName AS ToWarehouseName, TenantWarehouse.AddressLine1 AS ToWarehouseAddr1, TenantWarehouse.AddressLine2 AS ToWarehouseAddr2, TenantWarehouse.AddressLine3 AS ToWarehouseAddr3, TenantWarehouse.CountyState AS ToWarehouseCounty, TenantWarehouse.PostalCode AS ToWarehousePostcode, ISNULL(Orders.ShipmentAddressLine1, '') AS ShipmentAddressLine1, ISNULL(Orders.ShipmentAddressLine2, '') AS ShipmentAddressLine2, ISNULL(Orders.ShipmentAddressLine3, '') AS ShipmentAddressLine3, ISNULL(Orders.ShipmentAddressLine4, '') AS ShipmentAddressLine4, ISNULL(Orders.ShipmentAddressPostcode, '') AS ShipmentAddressPostcode, Orders.ShipmentAccountAddressId, Orders.DeliveryMethod, ISNULL(JobTypes.Name, '') + ': ' + ISNULL(JobSubTypes.Name, '') AS JobDescription, PProperties.AddressLine1 AS WorksPropertyAddress1, PProperties.AddressLine2 AS WorksPropertyAddress2, PProperties.AddressLine3 AS WorksPropertyAddress3, PProperties.AddressPostcode AS WorksPropertyPostcode, PTenants.TenantFullName AS WorksTenantFullName, PTenants.MobileNumber AS WorksTenantMobileNumber, PTenants.HomeTelephone AS WorksTenantHomePhone, PTenants.WorkTelephone1 AS WorksTenantWorkphone, Appointments.StartTime AS WorksStartTime, Appointments.EndTime AS WorksEndTime, Resources.FirstName + Resources.SurName AS WorksResourceName, PLandlords.LandlordFullname AS WorksLandlordName, PLandlords.MobileNumber AS WorksLandlordMobile, PLandlords.HomeTelephone AS WorksLandlordHomephone, PLandlords.WorkTelephone1 AS WorksLandlordWorkphone, Resources.ResourceId AS WorksAppointmentResourcesId, (SELECT STUFF ((SELECT '. ' + Notes AS 'data()' FROM OrderNotes WHERE (OrderID = Orders.OrderID) AND (IsDeleted IS NULL OR IsDeleted = 0) FOR XML PATH('')), 1, 1, '') AS Expr1) AS OrderNotes, CAST(Appointments.StartTime AS date) AS ScheduledDate, Orders.DateCreated, Orders.TransferWarehouseId FROM Orders INNER JOIN Tenants ON Orders.TenentId = Tenants.TenantId LEFT OUTER JOIN Account AS Accounts ON Orders.AccountID = Accounts.AccountID LEFT OUTER JOIN GlobalCountry AS GlobalCountries ON Accounts.CountryID = GlobalCountries.CountryID AND Tenants.CountryID = GlobalCountries.CountryID LEFT OUTER JOIN GlobalCurrency ON Accounts.CurrencyID = GlobalCurrency.CurrencyID AND Tenants.CurrencyID = GlobalCurrency.CurrencyID AND GlobalCountries.CountryID = GlobalCurrency.CountryID LEFT OUTER JOIN TenantLocations ON TenantLocations.WarehouseId = Orders.WarehouseId LEFT OUTER JOIN TenantLocations AS TenantWarehouse ON Orders.TransferWarehouseId = TenantWarehouse.WarehouseId LEFT OUTER JOIN SLAPriorits ON Orders.SLAPriorityId = SLAPriorits.SLAPriorityId LEFT OUTER JOIN AccountAddresses ON Accounts.AccountID = AccountAddresses.AccountID AND AccountAddresses.AddTypeDefault = 1 AND (AccountAddresses.IsDeleted = 0 OR AccountAddresses.IsDeleted is null) LEFT OUTER JOIN JobTypes ON JobTypes.JobTypeId = Orders.JobTypeId LEFT OUTER JOIN JobSubTypes ON JobSubTypes.JobSubTypeId = Orders.JobSubTypeId LEFT OUTER JOIN PProperties ON PProperties.PPropertyId = Orders.PPropertyId LEFT OUTER JOIN PTenants ON PTenants.CurrentPropertyCode = PProperties.PropertyCode AND PTenants.PTenantId = PProperties.CurrentPTenentId LEFT OUTER JOIN PLandlords ON PLandlords.LandlordCode = PProperties.CurrentLandlordCode AND PLandlords.PLandlordId = (SELECT TOP (1) PLandlordId FROM PLandlords WHERE (LandlordCode = PProperties.CurrentLandlordCode)) LEFT OUTER JOIN Appointments ON Appointments.OrderId = Orders.OrderID AND Appointments.IsCanceled = 0 AND Appointments.AppointmentId = (SELECT TOP (1) AppointmentId FROM Appointments WHERE (OrderId = Orders.OrderID) AND (Status = 0) AND (IsCanceled = 0) ORDER BY StartTime DESC) LEFT OUTER JOIN Resources ON Resources.ResourceId = Appointments.ResourceId
WHERE ("Tenants"."TenantId" = @SqlParamTenantId) AND ((CAST("Appointments"."StartTime" as DATE) = CAST(@SqlParamScheduleDate as DATE)) OR (Orders.OrderID = @SqlParamOrderId)) and (Orders.IsDeleted=0 or Orders.IsDeleted is null) Order By Resources.ResourceId

SELECT OrderDetails.OrderDetailID, OrderDetails.OrderID, OrderDetails.WarehouseId, OrderDetails.ProductId, OrderDetails.ProdAccCodeID, OrderDetails.Qty, OrderDetails.Price, OrderDetails.WarrantyID, OrderDetails.WarrantyAmount, OrderDetails.TaxID, OrderDetails.TaxAmount, OrderDetails.TotalAmount, ProductMaster.SKUCode, ProductMaster.Name, cast(ProductMaster.Description as varchar(500)),ProductMaster.BarCode, ProductMaster.UOMId, GlobalUOM.UOM, GlobalTax.TaxName, GlobalTax.TaxDescription, GlobalTax.PercentageOfAmount, OrderDetails.Notes as OrderDetailNotes, (select Sum(s.QtyProcessed) from dbo.OrderProcessDetails s Inner join dbo.orderProcesses p on p.OrderProcessID=s.OrderProcessId Where OrderDetailID = OrderDetails.OrderDetailID And p.InventoryTransactionTypeId=12 ) as QtyReturned FROM OrderDetails INNER JOIN ORDERS OD on OD.ORDERID= OrderDetails.ORDERID INNER JOIN ProductMaster ON OrderDetails.ProductId = ProductMaster.ProductId LEFT OUTER JOIN
GlobalUOM ON ProductMaster.UOMId = GlobalUOM.UOMId LEFT OUTER JOIN GlobalTax ON OrderDetails.TaxID = GlobalTax.TaxID AND ProductMaster.TaxID = GlobalTax.TaxID LEFT OUTER JOIN TenantWarranties ON OrderDetails.WarrantyID = TenantWarranties.WarrantyID WHERE (OrderDetails.IsDeleted=0 OR OrderDetails.IsDeleted IS NULL) AND
OrderDetails.ORDERID= @OrderId
